			) 
			
			```
		displayFolder: GrossProfit
		lineageTag: 4d229250-9ac8-4b40-a3e9-bcdf059d1fe2

	measure GrossProfit_CF = ```
			
			
			    var Month_Diff = [GrossProfit] - [GrossProfit_PM]
			    var Result = DIVIDE(Month_Diff, [GrossProfit_PM])
			
			    return 
